    <facet>
      <vocabularyID>LRE.expressionDescriptionFacetValues</vocabularyID>

    </facet>
    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770207098</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Park Histories</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Park-Geschichten</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Histoires de Parc</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Histories Do Parque</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Dati storici Del Parco</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ιστορίες πάρκων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Historias Del Parque</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">provides the text of out-of-print publications relating to the history of the National Parks -- how the parks were created and how they have evolved to the present day.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">stellt den Text der vergriffenen Publikationen in 
bezug auf die Geschichte der Nationalparks zur Verfügung -- wie die 
Parks hergestellt wurden und wie sie zum anwesenden Tag entwickelt 
haben.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">fournit le texte des publications épuisées 
concernant l'histoire des parcs nationaux -- comment les parcs ont 
été créés et comment ils ont évolué à aujourd'hui.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">fornece o texto das publicações out-of-print que
relacionam-se ao history dos parques nacionais -- como os parques 
foram criados e como evoluíram ao dia atual.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">fornisce il testo delle pubblicazioni esaurite 
concernente la storia dei parchi nazionali -- come i parchi sono stati
creati e come si sono evoluti ad oggi.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">παρέχει το κείμενο των out-of-print δημοσιεύσεων 
σχετικά με την ιστορία των εθνικών πάρκων -- πώς τα πάρκα 
δημιουργήθηκαν και πώς έχουν εξελιχθεί μέχρι την παρούσα ημέρα.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">proporciona al texto de publicaciones agotadas 
referente a la historia de los parques nacionales -- cómo los parques
fueron creados y cómo se han desarrollado a hoy.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
